ZXASCII
AUTO -1
PROG rotate
10 REM Rotate and Scale demo
20 PAPER 7: CLS: ELLIPSE INK 6;PAPER 8;200,100,100,50 FILL #16#1#0#0#0"S"#16#2#0#0#0"p"#16#3#0#0#0"e"#16#4#0#0#0"c"#16#5#0#0#0"B"#16#6#0#0#0"A"#16#7#0#0#0"S! "
30 WINDOW GRAB a$,0,100,50,200,100
40 SCREEN LOCK : LET angle=180: LET s=1: DEGREES
50 CLS : WINDOW PUT a$,0,(SCRw/2)-(s*200/2),(SCRh/2)-(s*100/2) ROTATE SIN angle*600 SCALE s
60 INC angle,1,0 TO 359: LET s=ABS(SIN(angle)*2)+0.1: WAIT SCREEN: GO TO 50
